room_title: Escape room "Cabin in the Woods" by Hochatown Escape Games in Broken Bow
room_address: 125 North Lukfata Trail Road, Broken Bow, OK 74728
room_description: You have experienced car trouble and with no phone reception, you must walk for help. You stumbled onto a cabin to call for assistance. However, when entering the door locks behind you preventing your escape. While inside you realize you have possibly entered upon a crime scene and your mission is to identify the killer and escape before he returns in one hour for his next victim.
